```{=html}

<div class="single-overview-wrapper">

  <div class="single-overview-intro">
    <div class="single-overview-title-image">
      <img src="../images/dct_measurement-coding.svg" width="100px" />
    </div>
    <div class="single-overview-introduction">
      This overview only contains the instructions for coding existing measurement instruments (e.g., for a systematic review). You can click a Unique Construct Identifier (UCID) to view the definition and all instructions for a construct, or <a href="../overview">check the full overview</a> for a table with the construct definitions and all instructions.
    </div>
  </div>

  <% for (const item of items) { %>

    <div <%= metadataAttrs(item) %> class="single-overview-view" >

      <span class="construct-view-construct-name listing-name">
        <%= item.dct.label %>
      </span>
      <span class="construct-view-ucid">
        (<a href="../<%= item.dct.id %>">❄️ <%= item.dct.id %></a>)
      </span>
      <span class="construct-single-overview-content">

      <% if (item.dct.measure_code.instruction) { %>
        <script>
          document.write(prepDCTtxt(`<%= item.dct.measure_code.instruction %>`));
        </script>
      <% } else { %>
        Not specified.
      <% } %></p>

    </div>

  <% } %>

</div>

```
